<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/2462f23e-b3b9-4f2c-ad37-ba52472cc6ca> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> _:b0__18163.
_:b0__18163 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((10.00 70.00,25.00 70.00,25.00 55.00,10.00 55.00,10.00 70.00))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
