_:b0__90545 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((5.51 69.85,28.60 69.85,28.60 53.89,5.51 53.89,5.51 69.85))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d8ec2980-752c-11ed-a51b-432755aaeed3> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://www.smhi.se/data/utforskaren-oppna-data/klimatolog_smhi.se>;
