<https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/caa55cab8f6f537b96379271ee1f3f14> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__2342.
_:b0__2342 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/author>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021006545>;
